  "body": "We will want a way to override params, like in beacon run.\r\nEspecially important here is GENESIS_FORK_VERSION.\r\nSo the chain.params will need to be an input here.\r\n\r\nThe direction I've been thinking lately is to do something like:\r\n- [x] create a IBeaconParams ssz type, `createIBeaconParams` to create IBeaconParams from a `Record<string, unknown>` / `Json` #1136 \r\n- [x] Use it to help create yargs `Options` if needed. All Options are `type: \"string\"`, will be parsed using `createIBeaconParams`\r\n- [x] Have a cli-wide params file. (should be copy-pastable from eg: https://github.com/eth2-clients/eth2-testnets/blob/master/shared/altona/config.yaml)\r\n- [x] Have all lodestar cli commands rely on this separate config file - Likely _every_ command needs the same IBeaconParams.\r\n- [x] First `lodestar-cli` bootup should require a config file, or have `lodestar init` to create it, or other similar behavior.\r\n\r\n_Originally posted by @wemeetagain in https://github.com/_render_node/MDIzOlB1bGxSZXF1ZXN0UmV2aWV3VGhyZWFkMjgxMzExNjg4OnYy/pull_request_review_threads/discussion_",
